    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "That's a great start. I want to make sure my students understand why this is so important. Can you add a section that explains why some people call this approach 'judicial activism' and why they think it's a problem for the democratic process? I want them to see the tension between the court's role and the will of the people.",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
